after conditioning the summer house some more (the running water issue, then pool cleaning, shed cleaning, gardening, severe cobweb removal, and a long etc), all of sudden i have the surgery for the metal-removal on my left leg tomorrow (two years waiting for it after the bike accident), so we need to pack and leave

